title: 2 bedroom 1st floor
posting_body: ['Nice first floor 2 bedroom apartment with plenty of closet space, just painted and put new floors.', ' Close to schools and transportation.', 'Heat is included in the rent.', 'Free laundry in the basement, free internet.', 'To save your valuable time and mine, I ask for this basic info before making an appointment as an effort to reduce unnecessary calls and trips for both you and me.', 'Would you please take a moment to e-mail me the following before I contact you back:Thanks!', '·  Name: __________________ __________________', '·  Phone: __________________', '·  Reason for Moving: ___________________________', '·  # of People & Relationship to you:__________________', '·  Intended lease term: (How long do you want to rent for?) _________', '·  Occupancy Date: _________', '·  Pets: _________', '·  Smoking: Y or N: _________', '·  How is your Credit: (Excellent, Good, Bad or Ugly) _____', '·  Do you have a Landlord Reference?', 'Y or N: _________', '·  What is/are your occupation(s)?', '_________', '·  Have you ever owned a home?', 'Y or N: _________', 'Gage Park, Fuller Park.']
